# Sequence Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant S as Streamlit App
    participant M as ML Model
    participant D as Data Processor
    U->>S: Upload Student Data
    S->>D: Preprocess Data
    D-->>S: Processed Data
    S->>M: Make Prediction
    M-->>S: Prediction Results
    S-->>U: Display Results
```
